INSERT INTO `blogposts` VALUES (101,'Zorvax\'s Dominion Log\r\n\r\n','<p>Hello, inhabitants of Earth.</p>\n\n<p>My name is Zorvax, envoy of the Zogthar Collective. Our scout vessel has entered your solar system and established a stable orbit. We come in peace… mostly. Curiosity brought us here. Your planet is unusually lively for one so small.</p>\n\n<p>I have been observing your broadcasts, your music, your arguments about whether folding or rolling pizza is superior. Fascinating. You are a species of endless variety.</p>\n\n<p>We will be making our presence known gradually. There is no need for alarm. Think of this as the beginning of a very long conversation.</p>\n\n<p>Until next time,<br>\nZorvax</p>'),(102,'Learning Your Ways','<p>Today I experimented with one of your communication platforms. I created a temporary profile and shared a few short messages. Within hours thousands of you responded.</p>\n\n<p>You are remarkably quick to connect with strangers who post interesting thoughts (or mysterious silhouettes). I received travel recommendations, recipes, poetry, and many questions about my “aesthetic.”</p>\n\n<p>It is… flattering. Your willingness to reach out is one of your better qualities. I have started a private list of kind messages to review when the long nights in orbit feel quiet.</p>\n\n<p>Thank you for being unexpectedly welcoming.<br>\nZorvax</p>'),(103,'A Taste of Earth Cuisine','<p>I acquired samples of several human foods through discreet means (no world leaders were involved, I promise).</p>\n\n<p>Observations so far:<br>\n– Coffee is powerful and smells like mornings should feel.<br>\n– The small round pastries called “donuts” are dangerously enjoyable.<br>\n– Spicy noodles make my sensory nodes tingle in a pleasant way.<br>\n– Chocolate is unfairly delicious. I may need to negotiate trade rights for it.</p>\n\n<p>Your culinary creativity is impressive. If diplomacy proceeds smoothly, perhaps we can arrange an exchange program: your recipes for some of our hydroponic fruits.</p>\n\n<p>Still savoring the aftertaste,<br>\nZorvax</p>'),(104,'Reflections on Feline Companions','<p>I have noticed that a very large portion of your digital content features small four-legged predators you call “cats.”</p>\n\n<p>They appear to rule many of your households. They sit on keyboards, knock objects off shelves, and receive unlimited admiration for doing so. I find this arrangement oddly charming.</p>\n\n<p>One video of a cat wearing sunglasses while sitting inside a cardboard box has now been replayed 1,847 times on my personal viewer. I do not understand why it brings me calm, but it does.</p>\n\n<p>Perhaps when we meet officially, I will request an audience with one of these feline dignitaries. They seem to have mastered the art of quiet authority.</p>\n\n<p>Respectfully studying,<br>\nZorvax</p>'),(105,'An Invitation','<p>The time for shadows is ending. In the coming days our ships will become visible in your skies—not as a threat, but as proof that you are not alone.</p>\n\n<p>We have watched your history: your wars, your art, your stubborn hope. You have survived ice ages, plagues, and your own mistakes. That resilience interests us more than conquest ever could.</p>\n\n<p>We propose a meeting. Not domination. Partnership. An exchange of knowledge, stories, music, perhaps even recipes. There is much we can learn from each other.</p>\n\n<p>If you are willing, look upward tonight. The first lights you see moving in formation are not stars. They are us, waiting politely for your reply.</p>\n\n<p>Until we speak face to… appendage,<br>\nZorvax</p>'),(106,'5QDrww0KEk','Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor'),(107,'AlJEaE5VN5','Lorem ipsu